The future of auto starts here





        POWER
    

        WE ARE AAM
    



AAM is a premier, global leader in the design, engineering, validation and manufacturing of driveline, metal forming, powertrain, and casting technologies for automotive, commercial and industrial markets. AAM has over 25,000 associates operating at more than 90 facilities in 17 countries to support our customers on global and regional platforms with a focus on quality, operational excellence and technology leadership.We are AAM and we have the POWER to move the world.Learn How We Do It





        POWER
    

        WE ARE AAM
    



AAM is a premier, global leader in the design, engineering, validation and manufacturing of driveline, metal forming, powertrain, and casting technologies for automotive, commercial and industrial markets. AAM has over 25,000 associates operating at more than 90 facilities in 17 countries to support our customers on global and regional platforms with a focus on quality, operational excellence and technology leadership.We are AAM and we have the POWER to move the world.Learn How We Do It




















